===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|gossib|lang=enm}}, {{term|godsib||a close friend or relation, a confidant|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|godsibb|lang=ang||godparent, sponsor}}, equivalent to {{compound|god|sib}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Someone who likes to talk about someone else’s private or personal business.
# Idle [[talk]] about someone’s [[private]] or [[personal]] matters, especially someone not present.
